      <title>德国极右翼政党因中国间谍重磅事件而失势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/german-spying-far-right-party-loses-ground-after-china-revelations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧洲议会选举的一项新民意调查中，极右翼德国另类选择党的支持率下降了两个百分点，这表明与中国情报部门有联系的指控正在损害该党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/german-spying-far-right-party-loses-ground-after-china-revelations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 06:54:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克拒绝在当地投票前确认选举日期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/sunak-refuses-to-confirm-election-date-ahead-of-regional-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相拒绝在本周关键地区投票之前确定大选日期，这些投票被视为保守党前景的风向标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/sunak-refuses-to-confirm-election-date-ahead-of-regional-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国任命资本市场资深人士担任财务主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/thailand-picks-capital-markets-veteran-pichai-as-finance-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛任命资本市场资深人士皮查伊·春哈瓦吉拉 (Pichai Chunhavajira) 为新任财政部长，此项任命或将缓解总理与央行在货币政策问题上的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/thailand-picks-capital-markets-veteran-pichai-as-finance-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 04:43:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国考虑缩减对中国投资的审查：《华尔街日报》</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/germany-mulls-scaling-back-scrutiny-of-chinese-investments-wsj</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》报道，德国正在考虑缩减政府加强对中国投资审查的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/germany-mulls-scaling-back-scrutiny-of-chinese-investments-wsj</guid>
